Cleaning data

# GPU
nama_gpu <- datapsd$GPU

# Membuat fungsi untuk mengubah nilai
ubah_nama_gpu <- function(nama_gpu) {
  if (grepl("Adreno", nama_gpu, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Adreno")
  } else if (grepl("Mali", nama_gpu, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Mali")
  } else if (grepl("Apple", nama_gpu, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Apple")
  } 
  else if (grepl("PowerVR", nama_gpu, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("PowerVR")
  }
  else {
    return("Lainnya")
  }
}

# Menggunakan fungsi untuk mengubah nilai dalam data
datapsd$GPU <- sapply(nama_gpu, ubah_nama_gpu)

# Processor
# Data nama processor awal
nama_processor <- datapsd$Processor

# Membuat fungsi untuk mengubah nilai
ubah_nama_processor <- function(nama_processor) {
  if (grepl("Deca-core", nama_processor, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Deca-core")
  } else if (grepl("Octa-core", nama_processor, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Octa-core")
  } else if (grepl("Quad-core", nama_processor, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Quad-core")
  } 
  else if (grepl("Dual-core", nama_processor, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Dual-core")
  } 
  else if (grepl("Hexa-core", nama_processor, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Hexa-core")
  } 
  else {
    return("Lainnya")
  }
}

# Menggunakan fungsi untuk mengubah nilai dalam data
datapsd$Processor <- sapply(nama_processor, ubah_nama_processor)

# rear
# Data nama processor awal
nama_rear <- datapsd$Rear

# Membuat fungsi untuk mengubah nilai
ubah_nama_rear <- function(nama_rear) {
  if (grepl("Dual camera", nama_rear, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Dual camera")
  } else if (grepl("Penta camera", nama_rear, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Penta camera")
  } 
  else if (grepl("Quad camera", nama_rear, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Quad camera")
  }
  else if (grepl("Single camera", nama_rear, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Single camera")
  }
  else if (grepl("Triple camera", nama_rear, ignore.case = TRUE)) {
    return("Triple camera")
  }
  else {
    return("Lainnya")
  }
}

# Menggunakan fungsi untuk mengubah nilai dalam data
datapsd$Rear <- sapply(nama_rear, ubah_nama_rear)

# main C
datapsd$MainC <- gsub("[^0-9.]", "", datapsd$MainC)
datapsd$MainC <- as.numeric(datapsd$MainC)

# front
datapsd$Front <- gsub("[^0-9.]", "", datapsd$Front)
datapsd$Front <- as.numeric(datapsd$Front)

datapsd$Size <- as.numeric(datapsd$Size)
datapsd$Price <- as.numeric(datapsd$Price)

ridge

library(glmnet)
## Warning: package 'glmnet' was built under R version 4.3.1
## Loading required package: Matrix
## Loaded glmnet 4.1-8
xtk <- data.matrix(datapsd[,c('Size','Processor','GPU','RAM','ROM','Battery','Rear')])
ytk <- datapsd$Price
cv.r<-cv.glmnet(xtk,ytk,alpha=0)

best.lr<-cv.r$lambda.min
bestridge<-glmnet(xtk,ytk,alpha=0,lambda=best.lr)
coef(bestridge)
## 8 x 1 sparse Matrix of class "dgCMatrix"
##                        s0
## (Intercept)  2.962608e+00
## Size         7.046475e-04
## Processor   -3.566945e-02
## GPU         -1.842954e-02
## RAM          4.668453e-01
## ROM          6.466363e-01
## Battery     -1.452666e-05
## Rear         4.511642e-03
# fungsi untuk cari rsquared
rsq<-function(bestmodel,bestlambda,x,y){
 #y duga
 y.duga <- predict(bestmodel, s = bestlambda, newx = x)

 #JKG dan JKT
 jkt <- sum((y - mean(y))^2)
 jkg <- sum((y.duga- y)^2)

#find R-Squared
rsq <- 1 - jkg/jkt
return(rsq) 
}

# R2 ridge
R2.ridge <- rsq(bestridge,best.lr,xtk,ytk)
R2.ridge
## [1] 0.4442529
#RSE ridge
train_predictionsr <- predict(bestridge,newx = xtk)
# Hitung residu (selisih antara prediksi dan nilai sebenarnya)
residualsr <- ytk - train_predictionsr
# Hitung varian residu
dfr <- length(ytk) - length(bestridge$beta)
residual_variancer <- sum(residualsr^2) / dfr
# Hitung RSE
rse.ridge <- sqrt(residual_variancer)
rse.ridge
## [1] 0.2701979
